com.facebook.buck.apple

Class XctoolRunTestsStep

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.apple.XctoolRunTestsStep
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Step

    public class XctoolRunTestsStep
extends Object
implements Step
    Runs xctool on one or more logic tests and/or application tests (each paired with a host application). The output is written in streaming JSON format to stdout and is parsed by XctoolOutputParsing.
